
BitSpirit ([tpl]lang-zh|比特精灵[/tpl]) is a freeware, closed source BitTorrent client by ByteLinker Inc. It is available for Microsoft Windows and written in C++.[ref]
</ref>
According to TorrentFreak, 1.996% of BitTorrent users are using BitSpirit.[ref]
</ref>

